This is one of the best TV shows ever made in the history of television industry encompassing all genres. Although, this TV show has a lot of crime and drama, some of its dialogues make you laugh more than most of the comedy series in the television industry. Every episode is unique and interesting in this five series TV show. The story moves at a very natural and realistic speed. This is one of the best works by Vince Gilligan till date. Everyone did superb acting especially Bryan Cranston and Aaron Paul. Superb dialogues, amazing story and excellent acting make this the best drama TV show.

A must watch for all!